OL,6,CG1967FThe final episode of Adam
OL,7,FAdamant airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1968FThe first edition of Look North
OL,10,F(from Leeds) airs on BBC One North.
OL,11,
OL,12,CG1972FThe 17th Eurovision Song Contest
OL,13,Fairs on BBC One, live from Usher Hall,
OL,14,FEdinburgh. Moira Shearer presented,
OL,15,Fwith Tom Fleming providing the
OL,16,Fcommentary.
OL,17,
OL,18,CG1973FThe pilot episode of Open All
OL,19,FHours airs on BBC Two (as part of the
OL,20,FSeven of One series). The pilot was
OL,21,Frepeated on BBC One on 31st July 1973.
