OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2003F30th anniversary edition of Look
OL,7,FNorth (Leeds) airs on BBC One
OL,8,FYorkshire.
OL,9,
OL,10,CG2009FThe first episode of Alan
OL,11,FWhicker's Journey of a Lifetime airs on
OL,12,FBBC Two. A four-part series in which
OL,13,Fveteran broadcaster Alan Whicker sets
OL,14,Foff on a world trip during which he
OL,15,Freflects on his life and career,
OL,16,Fbeginning in Venice, where he retraces
OL,17,Fhis steps from soldier to journalist
OL,18,Fand thence to the world of television.
