OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2018F50th anniversary edition of BBC
OL,7,FLook North airs on BBC One Yorkshire.
OL,8,FPresented by Harry Gration and Amy
OL,9,FGarcia, with Paul Hudson (weather).
OL,10,FMany former colleagues appeared,
OL,11,Fincluding Sophie Raworth, Philip Hayton
OL,12,Fand Tim Ewart. The programme was
OL,13,Fbroadcast live from Old Broadcasting
OL,14,FHouse, Woodhouse Lane, where it was
OL,15,Fbased from 1974 until 2004.
